READ ME 
# Metamask Browser Setup

This project guides you through installing and using the Metamask crypto wallet browser extension. Learn how to set up a wallet and connect it to decentralized apps (DApps).

## Contents

- [Installation](INSTALLATION.md)
- [Usage Guide](usage/connect_dapp.txt)
- Screenshots of the setup process
INSTALLATION 
# Installing Metamask Browser Extension

## Step 1: Install Metamask

1. Visit: https://metamask.io
2. Click "Download"
3. Choose your browser (Chrome, Firefox, Edge)
4. Add the extension to your browser

## Step 2: Set Up Your Wallet

1. Click the Metamask icon in the browser toolbar
2. Click "Get Started"
3. Choose "Create a Wallet"
4. Set a strong password
5. Write down your Secret Recovery Phrase

### ðŸš¨ WARNING:
Never share your recovery phrase. Anyone with it can access your wallet.

## Step 3: Done!

Youâ€™re ready to connect to DApps!
USAGE
How to Connect Metamask to a DApp

1. Open a DApp like https://uniswap.org
2. Click "Connect Wallet"
3. Choose "Metamask"
4. Your Metamask extension will pop up
5. Approve the connection
6. You're now connected!

